Changelog Entry

Date: 24 October 2025
Version: 1.1
Module: Menu Page – Christoffel Shop App
Change Type: Feature Addition

Description of Change:

Added functionality to calculate and display the average price of meals in each category (Starters, Mains, Desserts) on the Menu Page.

Implemented a getAveragePrice(category) function that computes the mean price from the proposed menu items for the selected category.

Updated the Menu Page UI to display the calculated average above each category’s meal list.

Ensured compatibility with dynamic user-added meals from the Filter Page.

Styling added for the average price display for clarity and consistency with the existing design.

File(s) Updated:

App.js

Impact:

Users can now see the average price per category, enhancing transparency and improving user experience when browsing menu items.

No impact on existing cart, checkout, or filter functionalities.
